依据String方程有

$$m\ddot w = F\frac{{{\partial ^2}w}}{{\partial {x^2}}}$$

以及边界条件

$$w(0,t) = w(L,t) = 0$$

令$w(x,t) = W(x){e^{i\omega t}}$,则有

$${\omega ^2}\frac{m}{F}W(x) + \frac{{{\partial ^2}W(x)}}{{\partial {x^2}}} = 0$$

解为

$$W(x) = A\cos \beta x + B\sin \beta x$$

其中${\beta ^2} = {\omega ^2}\frac{m}{F}$

代入边界条件，则有

$$W(0) = A = 0,\;\;W(L) = A\cos \beta L + B\sin \beta L = 0$$

依据行列式为0,有

$$A = 0,\;\;\beta = \frac{{n\pi }}{L},\;n = 1,2\dots$$

可得

$${\omega _n} = \frac{{n\pi }}{L}\sqrt {\frac{F}{m}} ,\;n = 1,2\dots$$

由

$${f_1} = \frac{\omega }{{2\pi }} = \frac{c}{{2L}}$$

可得

$$c = \sqrt {F/m}$$"><h2>5</h2><p>依据String方程有</p><p></p><div class="MathJax" display="block" style="text-align:center;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="13.319ex" height="5.095ex" ## 5

依据String方程有

$$m\ddot w = F\frac{{{\partial ^2}w}}{{\partial {x^2}}}$$

以及边界条件

$$w(0,t) = w(L,t) = 0$$

令$w(x,t) = W(x){e^{i\omega t}}$,则有

$${\omega ^2}\frac{m}{F}W(x) + \frac{{{\partial ^2}W(x)}}{{\partial {x^2}}} = 0$$

解为

$$W(x) = A\cos \beta x + B\sin \beta x$$

其中${\beta ^2} = {\omega ^2}\frac{m}{F}$

代入边界条件，则有

$$W(0) = A = 0,\;\;W(L) = A\cos \beta L + B\sin \beta L = 0$$

依据行列式为0,有

$$A = 0,\;\;\beta = \frac{{n\pi }}{L},\;n = 1,2\dots$$

可得

$${\omega _n} = \frac{{n\pi }}{L}\sqrt {\frac{F}{m}} ,\;n = 1,2\dots$$

由

$${f_1} = \frac{\omega }{{2\pi }} = \frac{c}{{2L}}$$

可得

$$c = \sqrt {F/m}$$
